---
import BaseLayout from "../../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — JTimes">
  <section class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <!-- Viewfinder corner brackets — top-left intentionally omitted, hero-rule stands in its place -->
      <div
        class="about-line absolute top-0 right-0 w-4 h-7 md:w-5 md:h-9 border-t border-r border-accent/30"
        style="animation-delay: 0ms;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="about-line absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-4 h-7 md:w-5 md:h-9 border-b border-l border-accent/30"
        style="animation-delay: 0ms;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>
      <div
        class="about-line absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-10 h-4 md:w-14 md:h-5 border-b border-r border-accent/30"
        style="animation-delay: 0ms;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></div>

      <div class="hero-rule mb-10"></div>

      <div class="space-y-16 md:space-y-20">
        <!-- P1: centered, larger -->
        <p
          class="about-line text-center text-xl md:text-2xl text-ink/80 leading-relaxed font-light
                 md:max-w-lg md:mx-auto"
          style="animation-delay: 100ms;"
        >
          Light multiplied by <span style="font-family: 'Waiting for the Sunrise', cursive;" class="text-accent/60">time</span>. That's what a photograph is.
        </p>

        <!-- P2: left-aligned -->
        <p
          class="about-line text-center md:text-left text-base md:text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed font-light
                 md:max-w-md md:ml-12"
          style="animation-delay: 250ms;"
        >
          I collect the moments that <span style="font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;" class="text-accent/60">dissolve</span> if you don't catch them&mdash;
          the weight of a glance, the echo of something unsaid,
          the way <span style="font-family: 'Nothing You Could Do', cursive;" class="text-accent/60">silence thickens</span> just before something begins.
        </p>

        <!-- P3: right-aligned -->
        <p
          class="about-line text-center md:text-right text-base md:text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed font-light
                 md:max-w-md md:ml-auto md:mr-12"
          style="animation-delay: 400ms;"
        >
          Between the click of a shutter and the stillness that follows,
          I gather <span style="font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;" class="text-accent/60">fragments</span>. Not to keep them. Just to say they happened.
        </p>

        <!-- P4: centered, wider tracking -->
        <p
          class="about-line text-center text-lg md:text-xl text-ink/80 leading-relaxed font-light
                 md:max-w-lg md:mx-auto tracking-wide"
          style="animation-delay: 550ms;"
        >
          Some people call it photography.<br />
          I call it <span style="font-family: 'Waiting for the Sunrise', cursive;" class="text-accent/60">borrowing time</span>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Colophon -->
      <div class="about-line mt-24 md:mt-32 text-center" style="animation-delay: 700ms;">
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-border/40 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted/50 tracking-wider">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/jtimes.visual/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Instagram</a>
          &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
          <a href="https://www.threads.net/@jtimes.visual" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Threads</a>
          &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
          <a href="https://github.com/jameslyu916-source" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-line {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: about-fade-up 0.8s ease-out both;
  }

  @keyframes about-fade-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
